The DCP (DNG Color Profile) files in this directory are sourced from the
RawTherapee project (https://github.com/Beep6581/RawTherapee) and contributed
by their respective authors. RawTherapee is distributed under the GNU General
Public License v3. The DCP files themselves are community-contributed works
created from color-target measurements and distributed within the RawTherapee
project for the benefit of open-source raw processing.

Principal DCP contributors include:
- Maciej Dworak (the majority of profiles in this collection)
- Lawrence Lee
- Alberto Griggio
- Thanatomanic
- Morgan Hardwood
- And other RawTherapee contributors

The color-target RAW files used to generate many of these profiles were
released by their photographers under the CC0 license
(https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/).

Redistribution of these DCP files is consistent with RawTherapee's own
practice of including them in their open-source distribution and packaging.
If you are a DCP author listed here and have concerns about redistribution,
please file an issue at https://github.com/vdavid/prvw.

Source: https://github.com/Beep6581/RawTherapee/tree/dev/rtdata/dcpprofiles
